title: CLEAR WATER BAY
description: Clear Water Bay is a quiet little town where Li Ming, Zhang Li, and Wang Hao live

title: LI MING
description: Li Ming is a compassionate high school teacher at OneTwoThree Elementary, known for his patience and understanding, and often serves as a confidante for his friends' troubles

title: ZHANG LI
description: Zhang Li is a lively community event organizer, always brimming with energy; her enthusiasm and creativity often inspire those around her

title: WANG HAO
description: Wang Hao is a reserved librarian, whose extensive knowledge and wisdom earn him great respect among his peers
